These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, security-guard, social-worker, dancer, fisherman, paramedic
7 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, guinea-pig, goldfish, frog, fish, pony
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the owner of the pony is between the freelancer and the electrician##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 5. the freelancer is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the social-worker is between the owner of the goldfish and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the security-guard##1
11. the fisherman is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the owner of the dog is the dancer##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the pony##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| Job   | electrician  | social-worker        | freelancer  | paramedic     | fisherman   | security-guard       | dancer   |
| Pet         | lizard   | pony | goldfish    | guinea-pig  | frog | fish | dog |

