.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: metal, r&b, jazz, d&b, classical, indie, house
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, epic, disaster, action, spy, zombie, musical
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, scooter, ship, train, trike
 1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of house##1
 6. the fan of metal is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the fan of metal is between the person watching musical movies and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
10. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of metal##1
12. the person driving the bus is the fan of r&b##1
13. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of metal##1
14. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person driving the train##1
15. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
16. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | indie | house      | d&b     | metal  | classical | jazz | r&b |
| Movie-Genre         | epic  | superhero | zombie | disaster | musical | action   | spy  |
| Transport     | roller   | train     | trike        | scooter  | ship   | car       | bus      |

