.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, milk, soy-milk, tea, water
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, american, russian, chinese, thai, polish, australian
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, chess, baking, singing, cooking, camping, traveling
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is the colombian##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the chinese##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the thai##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the australian##2
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
10. the russian is on the right of the polish##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is the colombian##1
12. the russian is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking water##1
15. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage    | coffee     | soy-milk   | tea        | fanta   | iced-tea     | milk     | water    |
| Nationality         | american    | chinese | colombian | thai | australian | polish | russian |
| Hobby   | hiking | cooking       | chess     | baking | singing   | camping    | traveling      |

