.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
7 different games are played: canasta, go, snooker, monopoly, poker, backgammon, mah-jongg
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, animation, drama, musical, scientific, zombie
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, old-henry, ritmeester, bongani, bluemaster, vegafina, pall-mall
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 5. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the vegafina-smoker is the person watching action movies##1
10. the montecristo-smoker is the person playing poker##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the pall-mall-smoker##1
12. the person playing go is the bluemaster-smoker##1
13. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
15. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Game          | go  | backgammon    | poker  | canasta | monopoly  | mah-jongg | snooker |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | animation | zombie   | drama   | scientific | action     | adventure |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | pall-mall   | montecristo | ritmeester  | old-henry   | vegafina    | bongani    |

