 3. the freelancer is the person drinking cola##1
 4. the firefighter is the vegafina-smoker##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking water is the journalist##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 8. the prince-smoker is the doctor##1
 9. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is the person drinking water##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the bolivar-smoker is between the doctor and the analyst##2
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the doctor##1
14. the swisher-smoker is the person drinking juice##1
15. the freelancer is on the left of the person drinking water##1
16. the vegafina-smoker is the person drinking coffee##1

