 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 5. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person traveling to rome and the person traveling to colone##2
 7. the person traveling to boston is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
