 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who likes black and the person who likes turquise##2
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 6. the person who likes emerald is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the person who likes black is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
