12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
13. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
15. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
16. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | tea      | mirinda | water     | coffee     | soy-milk   | milk |
| Movie-Genre       | superhero    | family | crime    | scientific | mystery     | adventure | martial-arts |
| Transport        | roller    | train | boat    | van    | car | snowmobile | tram |

